OL,7,FA Bristol doctor has called for a new
OL,8,Ffacility in the city where people who
OL,9,Fthink they've been spiked can get
OL,10,Ftested.
OL,12,FDr Tom Roberts, a lecturer at the
OL,13,FUniversity of Bristol and doctor at
OL,14,FSouthmead Hospital, said it would give
OL,15,Fthem more clarity over what had
OL,16,Fhappened.
OL,18,FMedics do not routinely test alleged
OL,19,Fvictims of spiking for drugs or their
OL,20,Fblood-alcohol level when they attend
OL,21,Fan emergency department.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/18
