OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,FDr Roberts spoke to ITV News West
OL,8,FCountry following the case of Simone
OL,9,FWhite, who experienced serious
OL,10,Fneurological problems after her drink
OL,11,Fwas reportedly spiked.
OL,13,FHe said: "I think there's definitely
OL,14,Fan expectation to reality mismatch.
OL,16,F"People come expecting clarity and
OL,17,Fdiagnostic testing, and for us to tell
OL,18,Fthem exactly what's going on, but it's
OL,19,Fjust not something that we're able to
OL,20,Fdo or provide."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/18
