OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,FIf you have been affected by any of
OL,8,Fthe issues raised in this report,
OL,9,Fthere is help available to you. Visit
OL,10,Fthe charity for support, resources and
OL,11,Fguidance. If you believe you have been
OL,12,Fa victim of crime, contact your local
OL,13,Fpolice force to report it.
OL,15,FIt follows by Dr Roberts and six
OL,16,Fothers in 2023, addressing the rising
OL,17,Freports of drink and injection spiking
OL,18,Fover the previous two years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/18
