OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,FHe worked with psychologist Dr Jo
OL,8,FDaniels to assess how a lack of
OL,9,Ftesting could leave victims feeling
OL,10,Fconfused and inhibit their recovery.
OL,12,F"A lot of it comes from the inability
OL,13,Fto form memories around the event.
OL,15,F"So most people are intoxicated with
OL,16,Falcohol or another substance and they
OL,17,Fmaybe don't remember what's happened.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
