FL,439,437,8ff,8ff,8ff,8ff
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F438A1718061656
OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,F"A lot of the potential trauma down
OL,8,Fthe line comes from that - this
OL,9,Finability to form memories, the
OL,10,Finability to form a clear timeline of
OL,11,Fwhat happened - and when your mind
OL,12,Ffills in the blanks, it generally does
OL,13,Fthat quite negatively.
OL,15,F"You can get a lot of thoughts like
OL,16,F'was I actually at risk from sort of
OL,17,Fphysical or sexual assault?' and these
OL,18,Fthings ruminate in your mind.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/18
