OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,F"For a small subset of people, those
OL,8,Fthoughts become quite severe. It
OL,9,Fbecomes a traumatic event and they
OL,10,Fhave a really significant
OL,11,Fpsychological impact," Dr Roberts said.
OL,13,FHe added that patients were routinely
OL,14,Fadvised to contact the police
OL,15,Fthemselves to make a report, but that
OL,16,Fdoctors could not do this for them.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/18
