OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,F"Police do attend the emergency
OL,8,Fdepartment, for things like sexual
OL,9,Fassault and physical assault, and
OL,10,Fthere are quite clear pathways for the
OL,11,Finvestigation of those things.
OL,13,F"In some ways, if there's been a clear
OL,14,Fsecondary crime committed, you're more
OL,15,Flikely to have available testing," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/18
