OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,FDr Roberts added that many clinicians
OL,8,Fhave also argued that testing a
OL,9,Fpatients will not change how they are
OL,10,Ftreated, so it isn't useful for
OL,11,Femergency medics.
OL,13,F"We see two groups of patients. There
OL,14,Fare those who come to the emergency
OL,15,Fdepartment overnight, acutely unwell,
OL,16,Fconfused and distressed because of
OL,17,Fwhat's going on.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
