CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F438A1718061656
OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,F"And then there's another group of
OL,8,Fpatients who come the next morning
OL,9,Fhaving woken up, disorientated, in
OL,10,Ftheir own bed. They come to the ED
OL,11,Fclinically well but looking for
OL,12,Fanswers.
OL,14,F"Then people are going back and forth
OL,15,Fto the police, and back to us trying
OL,16,Fto seek testing - but nowhere
OL,17,Froutinely does it," Dr Roberts
OL,18,Fexplained.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/18
