OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,FIn some cases, doctors might do blood
OL,8,Ftests to decide how to treat a
OL,9,Fpatient, but even if these tests are
OL,10,Fdone, the results can't be used as
OL,11,Fforensic evidence, he explained.
OL,13,FThat is not the only challenge. In the
OL,14,FUK, the majority of victims are spiked
OL,15,Fwith extra alcohol, making it
OL,16,Fdifficult to determine what they
OL,17,Fknowingly drank.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/18
