OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,F"You have to think about your blood-
OL,8,Falcohol level, the last time you
OL,9,Fdrank, how much you had to eat the
OL,10,Fprevious day, your normal alcohol
OL,11,Fconsumption
OL,13,F"That would be quite challenging to
OL,14,Funpick, so the busy emergency
OL,15,Fdepartment probably isn't the right
OL,16,Fplace for that to happen," he
OL,17,Fexplained.
OL,19,FA test centre for spiking victims in
OL,20,FBristol
