OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,FDr Roberts said he thought a special
OL,8,Ftesting centre could help give victims
OL,9,Fof spiking some clarity and certainty.
OL,11,F"What we believe is that there should
OL,12,Fprobably be some sort of community
OL,13,Fpathway available where you can get
OL,14,Ftested the next morning at 8am for a
OL,15,Frange of substances.
OL,17,F"But it's all about the psychological
OL,18,Fsupport as well. It's our role to
OL,19,Fpromote this and to think about what's
OL,20,Fbest for patients in the long-run.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/18
