OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,F"People come to the emergency
OL,8,Fdepartment because these things happen
OL,9,Fon a Friday night, Saturday night and
OL,10,Fwe're the only place open.
OL,12,F"So we're nowhere near a solution yet,
OL,13,Fbecause it all comes down to 'who's
OL,14,Fgoing to fund a service that doesn't
OL,15,Falready exist - in the current
OL,16,Feconomic climate?'"
OL,18,FNo record of new drugs being used
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/18
