OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,FDr Roberts added that, without
OL,8,Fregularly testing of spiking victims,
OL,9,Fit's difficult to spot emerging trends
OL,10,Fin which drugs are being used, or to
OL,11,Fidentify new substances.
OL,13,FHe explained: "Because we don't test,
OL,14,Fwe don't know what the problem is.
OL,16,F"We get people saying 'I've been
OL,17,Fspiked' and we say 'okay, we
OL,18,Funderstand' and then we manage them
OL,19,Fappropriately, but what we don't do is
OL,20,Froutinely measure it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/18
