OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,F"So, we've got no idea, A - what's
OL,8,Fbeen used to spike people, and B - how
OL,9,Fbig the problem is. There's huge scope
OL,10,Ffor more research. We'd like to do
OL,11,Fsome more where we trial testing and
OL,12,Freview what difference it makes.
OL,14,FIf you have been affected by any of
OL,15,Fthe issues raised in this report,
OL,16,Fthere is help available to you. Visit
OL,17,Fthe charity for support, resources and
OL,18,Fguidance. If you believe you have been
OL,19,Fa victim of crime, contact your local
OL,20,Fpolice force to report it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/18
