OL,3,CCalls for facility where people who
OL,4,Cthink they've been spiked can get
OL,5,Ctested
OL,7,F"But that's difficult research to do
OL,8,Fbecause the patients arrive in the
OL,9,Fmiddle of the night and they mightn't
OL,10,Fhave the capacity to consent to
OL,11,Ftesting.
OL,13,F"So even doing research in this area
OL,14,Fisn't straightforward, but it's
OL,15,Fsomething we're actively looking to
OL,16,Fdo."
